WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.498
Well family, I have a word for you.

00:00:02.498 --> 00:00:20.460
The Lord spoke to me again today and He said, 'Brandon, remember the word that I gave you over a year ago, warning you to tell the people that there was a great deception coming from celebrities.

00:00:20.840 --> 00:00:32.943
They would claim that they're born again and they're on fire for Me, but they are sent to cause deception and confusion in the body of Christ.

00:00:32.943 --> 00:00:40.658
' Not all the celebrities that you see in the near future are going to be truly of Me.

00:00:40.658 --> 00:00:55.846
I saw a plan from the enemy that these people have sold their soul to the devil and they are being instructed from the devil to say that they're born again Christians.

00:00:55.846 --> 00:01:38.524
And when they start to come out and say, 'Hey, we're Christians, it's all about Jesus, everything's exciting, we just gave our hearts to the Lord,' then all of a sudden, about five or six months into their salvation, or the radical transformation that they're going to proclaim they have, they start preaching a universal gospel—that every religion is the way to Heaven, that you can be a Buddhist, you can be a Muslim, or any of these different faiths around the world.

00:01:46.320 --> 00:02:02.008
They believe all these false gods are all the way to Heaven, that it's not just Jesus that gets you to Heaven, but you can have any religion, any belief is the way to the Father.

00:02:03.622 --> 00:02:08.799
And they start saying this stuff out of their mouth, and this is wrong.

00:02:08.799 --> 00:02:19.186
I'm here to tell you, when you hear this kind of teaching that there are other ways to Heaven other than Jesus Christ, run!

00:02:19.186 --> 00:02:26.839
The only way to the Father is the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:02:29.720 --> 00:02:30.460
And you say, 'Well, that's narrow-minded.

00:02:30.460 --> 00:02:34.389
' No, it's the Bible.

00:02:47.720 --> 00:02:48.040
That's the Bible, that's what the word of God says.

00:02:49.890 --> 00:02:54.044
And if you're a Christian, you only go by what the word of God says—the Bible, the B-I-B-L-E.

00:02:54.044 --> 00:02:55.493
That's the book for me.

00:02:55.493 --> 00:03:04.760
And if you're teaching anything other than the word of God, it's a false gospel.

00:03:04.760 --> 00:03:09.559
It's not Jesus, and it's the devil.

00:03:09.559 --> 00:03:15.474
So I've seen a great deception coming because of what's about to happen in Hollywood.

00:03:20.611 --> 00:03:31.040
The Lord stirred this up in me again, and there is a mighty move, a great supernatural move of the presence of the Lord that's about to take place in Hollywood.

00:03:31.040 --> 00:03:49.851
And the Lord showed me when I was driving around just a little bit ago, I was praying and the Lord spoke to me and He said, 'Brandon, I'm about to invade Hollywood with my presence.

00:03:49.851 --> 00:04:09.880
As you see these fires, as you see this stuff going on in Hollywood, in California, my presence, my Shekinah glory, just like it did in Azusa Street, is going to touch Hollywood one last time with a great grace explosion.

00:04:09.880 --> 00:04:29.736
' To the people who are awake right now and you live in Hollywood, you live in Los Angeles—I told you about the people that if you're not hearing them to flee, but the Lord told me, He said, 'Brandon, that's not for everybody.

00:04:29.736 --> 00:04:34.500
' I want you to listen to me.

00:04:34.500 --> 00:04:44.337
There's going to be a mighty moving revival, a mighty move of the presence of the Lord on Hollywood.

00:04:44.337 --> 00:04:57.027
On the people who are the farthest, there is a shaking that's going to take place that's going to awaken Hollywood.

00:04:59.959 --> 00:05:05.044
And you will see a great move of the Spirit of the Lord on Rodeo Drive.

00:05:05.044 --> 00:05:14.600
You will see a great move of the Spirit of the Lord all throughout the Hollywood Hills and the celebrities.

00:05:18.690 --> 00:05:31.039
But not every single celebrity that you hear that's going to get radically saved in this timeframe is going to be one that you can listen to just because they proclaim it.

00:05:31.039 --> 00:05:33.409
Let's see the fruit.

00:05:33.409 --> 00:05:37.190
The fruit will demonstrate the word of God.

00:05:42.080 --> 00:05:42.355
The word and the fruit will go hand in hand.

00:05:51.830 --> 00:05:54.143
The fruit of the life of the celebrity—I'm trying to tell you—don't just follow them because they give you lip service.

00:05:56.129 --> 00:06:06.571
I saw pop stars, major name pop stars, that all of a sudden are going to get radically changed, and some of them really will.

00:06:06.571 --> 00:06:11.213
There will be a great shifting in celebrity.

00:06:11.213 --> 00:06:19.080
I saw reality TV people are going to become radically born again.

00:06:19.080 --> 00:06:42.733
I saw them having small groups in their houses—in mega-houses, these big homes—with all kinds of celebrities coming to these mega-houses and getting the word of God because they couldn't go to a church because it's too much of a distraction.

00:06:51.273 --> 00:07:02.485
So I saw them having Bible studies in the privacy of their homes because they couldn't go to churches because of their name and because people were trying to mess with them, but they were truly hungry and they were truly looking for Jesus.

00:07:04.180 --> 00:07:20.069
And when this happens, they will sit in these Bible studies and I saw the presence of the Lord just like it was in Acts chapter 2, when the mighty rushing wind came in and filled the house, and you will see a Holy Ghost fire on these homes.

00:07:24.160 --> 00:07:24.970
And when the Holy Ghost fire comes on these homes, you're going to see a radical transformation.

00:07:24.970 --> 00:07:26.713
For some, it's coming.

00:07:26.713 --> 00:07:37.424
A major move of the presence of God is coming on some homes in the Hollywood Hills, and I saw it.

00:07:37.424 --> 00:07:40.060
It's going to happen quickly and suddenly.

00:07:40.060 --> 00:07:47.586
As you see these fires and as you see these things taking place, everyone says, 'Well, it's judgment.

00:07:47.586 --> 00:07:51.714
' No, I told you it's a shaking to awaken.

00:07:57.366 --> 00:07:59.760
What is He waking people up to?

00:07:59.760 --> 00:08:00.120
Him.

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:02.040
Seed time and harvest.

00:08:12.633 --> 00:08:12.896
It's happening right before your face.

00:08:12.896 --> 00:08:24.119
The sowing to the bad politicians, the sowing to the bad senators in the house and changing the government there because they put in reprobate-minded people there.

00:08:40.246 --> 00:08:40.652
That's what's happening in Hollywood right now, because they sow to the flesh, and when you sow to the flesh, you reap corruption.

00:08:40.652 --> 00:08:47.555
It's not God's judgment on Hollywood right now, folks; this is a shaking to awaken because of bad decisions in seed time and harvest.

00:08:48.149 --> 00:08:59.679
So what I'm trying to tell you is, as you see the fires, as you see these flames, I know there will be some people...

00:08:59.679 --> 00:09:04.427
because you were living in those areas, you should have fled.

00:09:04.427 --> 00:09:27.515
If they lost their house, they lost their property and you're a believer and the Lord spoke to you, that's what I was trying to refer to you, to try to spur you to say, 'Listen, if the Lord's telling you to leave these areas, leave.

00:09:27.515 --> 00:09:35.386
' But if you're called to stay there, and you know just like that one man I saw...

00:09:35.386 --> 00:09:55.200
his house—he was a Christian and it was on the beach or whatever it was, I don't know if it was fake or whatever but it looked real—and he was on there telling a testimony about how his house was spared and everybody's house around him was burned up.

00:09:55.200 --> 00:09:59.630
That's the person who knows the authority of the believer.

00:09:59.630 --> 00:10:10.120
That's the person who understands their covenant and their rights of how to believe by faith and say, 'Listen, thus far and no further!

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:13.066
Satan, you're not touching my house.

00:10:13.066 --> 00:10:17.089
You're not going to touch and burn up my house.

00:10:17.089 --> 00:10:31.160
' Put the olive oil on your shoes that represents the blood of Jesus and march around your house, and no calamity will come nigh your home.

00:10:31.160 --> 00:10:33.947
That's what I'm talking about.

00:10:33.947 --> 00:10:41.110
If you don't have the faith to believe that, you should get out of there like Lot, leave.

00:10:41.110 --> 00:10:50.216
But there will be a remnant of you that stay and you'll be the ones that are the light in the darkness.

00:10:50.444 --> 00:10:53.411
You say, 'Well, I can't afford to leave.

00:10:53.411 --> 00:10:57.105
' Well, if you're not called to leave, that's fine.

00:10:57.105 --> 00:11:00.876
Pray a bloodline around your house is what I'm trying to tell you.

00:11:00.876 --> 00:11:12.423
Use your faith; no weapon formed against you—when there's earthquakes and divers places and you're in that divers place, no weapon formed against you is going to prosper.

00:11:13.085 --> 00:11:17.765
You have to use your faith for where you're at.

00:11:17.765 --> 00:11:28.820
But know that sometimes God's called you to stand in there, because if everybody's gone, who's going to be the light in that darkness?

00:11:28.820 --> 00:11:32.445
That's you, ladies and gentlemen.

00:11:32.445 --> 00:11:41.400
I believe there's some of you that will be called there, but if you're not able to believe, you need to leave.

00:11:41.400 --> 00:11:45.531
That's what I was trying to tell you.

00:12:01.120 --> 00:12:01.510
Okay, so Portland, these major cities that I've seen a great shaking coming...

00:12:01.510 --> 00:12:12.542
there's a great shaking with the celebrities, the NBA, the NFL, the major hockey leagues and the NHL, or whatever, all of them.

00:12:25.247 --> 00:12:25.535
I'm telling you, the Lord said even the ones that seem untouchable, the ones in the far left corner, He's calling you right now.

00:12:25.535 --> 00:12:32.600
He's calling you right now and He's giving one last call, even for the richest of the rich.

00:12:32.600 --> 00:12:42.930
He's giving one last call for the poorest of the poor and He's trying to tell you that you're running out of time.

00:12:46.399 --> 00:12:46.834
And the shaking to awakening is fixing to hit Hollywood.

00:12:46.834 --> 00:12:48.175
But what's the awakening?

00:12:48.175 --> 00:12:52.800
That's the part that you all need to get excited about.

00:12:54.230 --> 00:12:55.048
The shaking is happening for the awakening.

00:12:55.048 --> 00:12:56.275
What is the awakening?

00:12:56.275 --> 00:13:02.800
When people start to look and go, 'What's going on around us?

00:13:02.800 --> 00:13:04.719
Everything's burned up around us.

00:13:04.719 --> 00:13:05.426
What's happening?

00:13:05.426 --> 00:13:16.547
' The shaking, the earthquakes, all kinds of weirdness that's going on in this world right now, all the news and the corruption—it's shaking people.

00:13:16.547 --> 00:13:24.940
But we've not even touched just a little bit of this sliver of what's about to take place.

00:13:24.940 --> 00:13:29.850
Fires are nothing compared to what I've seen coming, folks.

00:13:29.850 --> 00:13:34.812
I've seen some very dark and hard times for some folks.

00:13:34.812 --> 00:13:45.978
They're going to wake up because the Lord said, 'It's not your life, you didn't go to hell, so you still have breath in your lungs, you still got a chance.

00:13:45.978 --> 00:14:21.210
' So He would rather some of these people lose everything around them and get shook to awaken—not to be 'woke,' but to be awake in Jesus, so that you have your eyes opened, your eyes of your understanding, according to Ephesians, that your eyes of your understanding would be enlightened, that you would know the hope of your calling, that you would know what He's done for you—that He died on the cross, He suffered, He paid the penalty of sin.

00:14:21.210 --> 00:14:29.440
He did it all for you so that you don't have to go to a devil's hell.

00:14:29.440 --> 00:14:46.720
Every single one of you have the opportunity right now, if you still have air in your lungs and you're able to listen to me right now, to know you can see that Jesus Christ is coming.

00:14:46.720 --> 00:14:49.220
You're able to see it right now.

00:15:04.003 --> 00:15:04.261
You have that opportunity to accept Jesus Christ today.

00:15:10.671 --> 00:15:16.760
But I'm telling you, there's a great revival coming to Los Angeles, there's a great revival coming to all of California, all up the western coast and all the eastern coastlines.

00:15:16.760 --> 00:15:23.200
There's a great shaking, though, that will take place to awaken.

00:15:28.299 --> 00:15:28.639
The only way to Heaven is Jesus Christ.

00:15:34.412 --> 00:15:34.639
The only way to the Father is Jesus Christ.

00:15:34.639 --> 00:15:49.333
So know that when you see all these celebrities that are about to get born again and you see all these people that are getting radical for Jesus, watch their fruits for a season.

00:15:49.333 --> 00:15:50.996
Because the young people...

00:15:50.996 --> 00:15:56.009
the Lord told me this was a plan to try to snare the young generation.

00:15:56.009 --> 00:16:06.305
The older generation will be able to discern and filter a lot better than the younger generation—the 15 to 30-year-olds.

00:16:06.305 --> 00:16:13.059
You've got that younger generation that already needs a shepherd; they don't have a lot of leading spiritually.

00:16:13.059 --> 00:16:17.946
So they're going to be so easily influenced because of the celebrity of who they are.

00:16:17.946 --> 00:16:26.224
And all of a sudden, they're the pop star that's automatically radically born again, and you're going, 'Whoa, this is so cool!

00:16:26.224 --> 00:16:31.021
' and you're listening to everything they say because they're okay now.

00:16:31.021 --> 00:16:36.844
Do you see what I'm trying to tell you?

00:16:36.844 --> 00:16:48.209
And all of a sudden, they're feeding a little poison, and then they give you a big spoonful of it.

00:16:48.209 --> 00:16:59.275
I'm trying to tell you all, you're going to have to be very discerning in these hours ahead for what's about to take place.

00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:10.364
And we rejoice with our brothers and sisters when they get born again, but we monitor their fruit.

00:17:26.169 --> 00:17:32.125
And if they start preaching a different kind of gospel, other than Jesus is the way and that He died and rose again on the third day and is seated at the right hand of the Father, run.

00:17:32.125 --> 00:17:37.735
You have to realize the Bible says, 'His words are a lamp unto my feet and a light unto my path.

00:17:38.264 --> 00:17:45.232
I will hide His word in my heart that I might not sin against You, Lord.

00:17:45.232 --> 00:17:49.526
' And that's in Psalms.

00:17:49.526 --> 00:18:01.390
I just want you to know that it's the word of God that should be the foundation for everything you do in your life.

00:18:02.600 --> 00:18:07.947
And as long as you have that word, His word is priority in your life, and prayer.

00:18:07.947 --> 00:18:13.280
Prayer and the word should go hand in hand.

00:18:18.510 --> 00:18:20.130
And as you pray, you obey what He's telling you to do.

00:18:20.130 --> 00:18:27.400
As you read the word, you follow what the Bible tells you to do.

00:18:34.926 --> 00:18:35.360
And as you seek Him daily, you'll find Him.

00:18:37.720 --> 00:18:44.080
The Bible says that those that seek Him will find Him; those that knock, the door will be opened unto them.

00:18:45.086 --> 00:18:50.788
And I'm telling you, folks, it's not hard; it's a day-to-day relationship.

00:18:55.120 --> 00:18:56.939
You work out your salvation with fear and trembling, for the fear of the Lord is the beginning of wisdom.

00:19:03.273 --> 00:19:06.220
You have to fear the Lord and know that God is merciful and He's great and His majesty is holy.

00:19:06.220 --> 00:19:15.060
But I long for Him, I want to know the Father intimately today.

00:19:16.816 --> 00:19:20.080
You say, 'I can't do that, I have sin.

00:19:20.080 --> 00:19:24.039
' Repent of it and walk on.

00:19:24.039 --> 00:19:33.017
Take communion daily and just go before Him and say, 'Father, I want to sit at Your throne.

00:19:33.017 --> 00:19:44.256
' You know, there are times He says, 'Welcome back, Brandon,' as I walk in and I praise Him and I get before Him.

00:19:44.256 --> 00:19:46.695
'Welcome back, son.

00:19:46.695 --> 00:20:13.069
' He's already dwelling inside of me, He's already living on the inside of every single one of you if you've received Him by faith, but there is a difference between this and being in the throne room.

00:20:13.069 --> 00:20:22.680
There is a tangible Shekinah glory that will come and fill your house.

00:20:22.680 --> 00:20:26.572
And I believe He wants to do that for you.

00:20:26.572 --> 00:20:35.180
The Bible says that He's no respecter of persons, and what He'll do for one, He'll do for another.

00:20:35.180 --> 00:20:43.375
But He is a respecter of faith and He's a respecter of those that seek Him.

00:20:51.944 --> 00:20:59.200
So that implies automatically that He's wanting you to seek Him.

00:20:59.200 --> 00:21:01.559
How desperate are you?

00:21:01.559 --> 00:21:03.310
We raise puppies a lot.

00:21:03.310 --> 00:21:10.946
You can see the ones that thrive, that are really hungry, versus the ones that have given up.

00:21:10.946 --> 00:21:25.279
They call it 'fading puppy syndrome' a lot of times, and the mother dog will lick the puppy and try to spur it to be alive.

00:21:25.279 --> 00:21:30.653
But if that puppy doesn't have a latch-on and a fight to want to live, it dies.

00:21:30.653 --> 00:21:37.943
But if that puppy is thriving and it's hungry and it wants to live...

00:21:37.943 --> 00:21:44.800
how bad is your 'want to' live?

00:21:44.800 --> 00:21:52.999
How bad and how desperate are you for change in your life?

00:21:54.049 --> 00:22:09.060
Are you like that little puppy that doesn't want to live, where you try to sustain its life but it doesn't have that 'want to' inside of itself?

00:22:31.840 --> 00:22:33.038
It just falls off and dies.

00:22:33.038 --> 00:23:01.152
Or you can be the thriving puppy that's just nursing and pulling and trying to get substance to keep their life alive.

00:23:01.152 --> 00:23:03.168
In Christ, be that!

00:23:03.168 --> 00:23:08.649
Be that person that is seeking Him that desperately.

00:23:08.649 --> 00:23:12.600
How bad do you want your life to change?

00:23:15.089 --> 00:23:16.680
You have to have a fight inside of you.

00:23:25.051 --> 00:23:25.365
You have to have a fight and say, 'I refuse to stay the same.

00:23:32.080 --> 00:23:36.280
I refuse to not have one more day without a fresh touch from Jesus.

00:23:36.280 --> 00:23:40.279
' I need a fresh touch from Jesus today.

00:23:40.279 --> 00:23:44.773
I'm desperate for more of Him.

00:24:05.180 --> 00:24:05.533
And as you're crying out for Him, you will find Him.

00:24:05.533 --> 00:24:10.846
But it's not going to be the one that's just lazy.

00:24:10.846 --> 00:24:13.840
How bad is your 'want to'?

00:24:13.840 --> 00:24:17.240
How bad is your desperation?

00:24:17.240 --> 00:24:21.180
How thirsty, how hungry are you for change?

00:24:21.180 --> 00:24:27.070
Because those that seek Him will find Him.

00:24:34.100 --> 00:24:34.455
The Bible says it's a promise.

00:24:34.455 --> 00:24:40.051
His word works all the time if you work His word.

00:24:40.051 --> 00:24:51.440
Get that word down inside of your heart today and it will change you from the inside out.

00:24:51.440 --> 00:24:54.632
There's levels of hunger, ladies and gentlemen.

00:24:58.300 --> 00:25:09.800
You could see a homeless person that hasn't eaten in a couple of days and they are starving; they need food so bad.

00:25:09.800 --> 00:25:20.731
But you walk by and you haven't eaten just in a couple of hours and you're going, 'Man, I'm hungry.

00:25:20.731 --> 00:25:23.553
' There's levels of hunger.

00:25:23.553 --> 00:25:29.179
There's a level of desperation for food that you'll do anything you can to sustain life.

00:25:29.179 --> 00:25:34.220
How bad is your 'want to' change in these last days?

00:25:34.220 --> 00:25:37.200
Are you just satisfied with the status quo?

00:25:50.736 --> 00:25:51.074
Because if you are, you will not be hungry enough to want to change.

00:25:51.074 --> 00:26:07.087
I'm trying to tell you there's that desperation that whenever you see your life's going to hell in a handbasket—it's all around you, everything's falling apart—you say, 'I need more of Him!

00:26:07.087 --> 00:26:08.432
I need more of Him!

00:26:08.432 --> 00:26:11.834
' and I'm desperate for Him every day.

00:26:11.834 --> 00:26:18.087
I'm just confident enough that if I seek Him, I'll find Him.

00:26:20.211 --> 00:26:20.703
And you know what He does?

00:26:24.812 --> 00:26:26.780
The Bible says that He is a rewarder of those that diligently seek Him.

00:26:26.780 --> 00:26:32.460
He'll reward you with open arms as you seek Him today.

00:26:45.609 --> 00:26:46.465
I pray this message blessed you.

00:26:48.475 --> 00:26:56.360
I pray that as a Watchman, I'm telling you something so you're being prepared, so you're not caught off guard for what's coming.

00:27:13.115 --> 00:27:13.370
I just want so badly for you to get excited and on fire for Him.

00:27:14.840 --> 00:27:16.725
I appreciate you watching this video today.

00:27:16.725 --> 00:27:19.120
Let me pray for y'all.

00:27:20.720 --> 00:27:24.460
Father, right now in the name of Jesus, they are hungry.

00:27:24.460 --> 00:27:34.360
I believe maybe this just fanned their flame just a little bit to get them to latch on.

00:27:34.360 --> 00:27:42.691
Be that puppy that's not fading, that latches on and says, 'I need a touch from Jesus.

00:27:42.691 --> 00:27:46.973
I need a touch from my risen Savior today.

00:27:46.973 --> 00:28:04.039
' Just like the woman with the issue of blood that reached out and grabbed the hem of His garment—she was desperate and she said, 'If I could just lay hold of the hem of His garment, I'll be made whole.

00:28:04.039 --> 00:28:06.364
' Touch His garment today.

00:28:14.531 --> 00:28:17.806
All you have to do is reach out by faith and say, 'God, I'm desperate for you, I'm thirsty for you.

00:28:17.806 --> 00:28:23.420
You are the living water; come and fill me once again, oh God.

00:28:23.420 --> 00:28:29.964
Come and fill me to the overflow of my soul.

00:28:29.964 --> 00:28:35.269
' I need a fresh touch from You today, Lord.

00:28:36.394 --> 00:28:37.519
I need a drink.

00:28:40.400 --> 00:28:40.780
I'm thirsty, Jesus, I am thirsty.

00:28:40.780 --> 00:28:45.279
Won't you come and fill me?

00:28:45.279 --> 00:28:49.520
Those earthly things have left me dry.

00:28:51.120 --> 00:28:54.764
You have to say it: only You can satisfy.

00:28:54.764 --> 00:29:00.853
All I want is more of You.

00:29:00.853 --> 00:29:04.949
Nothing I desire, Lord, but more of You.

00:29:04.949 --> 00:29:10.160
I want to know Him more.

00:29:18.304 --> 00:29:29.920
So Father, we just thank You, Lord, that we have a fresh touch from You today, that we're not snared by the plans of the wicked, but we are confident that You will sustain us.

00:29:29.920 --> 00:29:33.583
I thank You, Father, for a supernatural touch today.

00:29:33.583 --> 00:29:39.930
Thank You, Father, for your supernatural abundance of your presence on us today.

00:29:56.813 --> 00:29:57.000
